    "## 7. Summary\n",
    "\n",
    "### What makes Mamba work:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Component | Purpose | Effect |\n",
    "|-----------|---------|--------|\n",
    "| Pre-Norm | Stabilize training | Better gradient flow |\n",
    "| Expansion | Increase capacity | More parameters |\n",
    "| SiLU Gate | Gating mechanism | Adaptive computation |\n",
    "| Selective SSM | Content-based reasoning | O(N) attention |\n",
    "| Residual | Gradient flow | Deeper networks |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Key advantages over Transformers:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Linear time complexity** - O(N) instead of O(N²)\n",
    "2. **Constant inference** - No KV cache needed\n",
    "3. **Content selection** - Can learn what to ignore\n",
    "4. **Similar quality** - Matches transformer on many tasks\n",
    "\n",
